data.description: Fall in love with the scenery on your way to view this adorable farm house style property with endless potential and tons of space. Sitting on nearly 12 acres and just a mile from the gorgeous 4R Winery makes for a perfect location for an Airbnb. Just down the road from Red River Motorcycle Trails. Land is perfect for hunting! This property falls in Saint Jo ISD or Muenster ISD so the choice is yours! Very well foam insulated and a huge attic! The back porch looks out over a large backyard. A creek runs through the back of the property as well.
